data.title: What's it like to live in Jämtland, Sweden?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): I adore it.

This is the real picture book Sweden you see in children’s books. Hilly landscapes dotted with red farm houses, deep blue lakes, and wild forests up and down all the hills, to the blue horizon.
